Package it.unipr.sowide.actodes.executor

Class ExecutorActor

java.lang.Object
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.actor.Actor
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.executor.ExecutorActor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Runnable
public class ExecutorActor
extends Actor
implements Runnable
The ExecutorActor class defines the executor actor of an actor space, i.e., the actor that manages the execution of the other actors (excluding the other special actor, i.e., the service provider) of the actor space.
